\begin_layout Itemize
(Cumulative) distribution function
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F\left(x\right)=P\left(X\leq x\right)=P\left(\left\{ \omega\in\Omega:X\left(\omega\right)\leq x\right\} \right).
\]

